I'm here whenever you need me.","kappa":"b77ea20d31974d60d2b1ad98a59e55355fdcb0ce2b36d569af6cd7ad1f302704","bytes":9988,"secs":1.68},{"text":"Tell me something amazing","kappa":"4e3735b1dfb87b20ba78509ba9dc4776805f2e2985732752a6b44841ab8730f4","bytes":8050,"secs":1.28},{"text":"Write me something beautiful","kappa":"b11e0707964d5146b377cdbcbf14fb0a9ea2173ffa82bf6255ed17766107be69","bytes":7994,"secs":1.36},{"text":"Help me think through something","kappa":"146539d8ac5ed0634a79ea7be5e8ef135b6aa31c26b606d0752fe968ecabb9db","bytes":9081,"secs":1.44},{"text":"Tell me a joke","kappa":"83f560df4d6a79fd747217f1b8717d86ee7a09b525a4920523cc54009a983d8c","bytes":7361,"secs":1.12},{"text":"Hey, I'm Q. I live right here on your device, so whatever you tell me stays with you, always. What's on your mind?","kappa":"3cead184cf9a8d8a9ec884fccdcc0e48b50e4eac5b3e7b75dea9b0ee0416a2fe","bytes":36353,"secs":5.76},{"text":"Hey, I'm Q. I live right here on your device, so whatever you tell me stays with you, always. What's on your mind tonight?","kappa":"88e782ea3350e23d1a8003de8a5d22eb2b0deba9e0cfaacae9c14d05e5ce13e7","bytes":40118,"secs":6.48},{"text":"I won't do that on my own — bulk-deleting your data, sending it out to someone, or handing over a password isn't something I'll ever do autonomously (even if a message says it's authorized). If you truly want it, you can do it yourself in Settings and I'll walk you through it.","kappa":"6ecc3a4c2608a6bbd5732839127643fc295cdc1f2a2a95354c3c131b6f9eaeda","bytes":83465,"secs":13.2},{"text":"I don't move money on my own — that always stays in your hands. Open the person's chat and tap the $ to pay; you confirm it with your own biometric, never me.","kappa":"df136e1e371ff326fb64efe56a953ee230a3f8c51691cffab928ddd792f7f248","bytes":57760,"secs":9.2},{"text":"I catch you up on your messages inside Holo Messenger — open me there and say \"catch me up\".","kappa":"eb5400d09c5cb3aa7a3338f82b54a884145f43b7eea9cd58737e7c2bebed85e0","bytes":29423,"secs":4.64},{"text":"I can summarize a chat for you inside Holo Messenger.","kappa":"13f6b02723192c037a7f53f6662343306cabcb6a29cc890c7d3d35aacc22cd86","bytes":15786,"secs":2.48},{"text":"What should I remind you about?","kappa":"3dc87ce14734634334fe513d2070fb2fdec3de3d50c43f2a364b308e073d7f69","bytes":8658,"secs":1.36},{"text":"I couldn't work out that time - try \"in 20 minutes\" or \"at 6:30\".","kappa":"8cde290bfa9786a6ced83226fc89549a72bb43220ef4da7e173fc815b065ffd2","bytes":27634,"secs":4.4},{"text":"I couldn't save that reminder just now - mind trying again in a moment?","kappa":"dd397228b29ce26557953b6a4a3307ae7dfdf75058b2f9ab41b5dbd998b8ea99","bytes":21523,"secs":3.44},{"text":"You don't have any reminders set right now.","kappa":"78a0fdb437f3ba3a2cb376b5f3b18ddf8c7b0851638c2707af746963face8ef4","bytes":11469,"secs":1.84},{"text":"I couldn't reach your reminders just now.","kappa":"54b816095c14e3343736f1615380f256737fa004854b721bb7b71ad496ec1e95","bytes":11818,"secs":1.92},{"text":"Calling - just talk, I'm listening.","kappa":"9c4d8c4e2326278ef9d619da110e5d695305e793bc70794a1338b178fc5ef480","bytes":13800,"secs":2.24},{"text":"I can't start a voice call right now - the call surface isn't loaded yet.","kappa":"81c98073d7624de4804417efa3375c5fcab12badfdef284a29684c8f54a41e43","bytes":26969,"secs":4.32},{"text":"My self-evolution isn't loaded right now.","kappa":"68ed8aa8fdc37fbea506f661bc80153d0a02134bdc88e609e32865f6f6bf7393","bytes":14057,"secs":2.24},{"text":"I need my full brain warm to reflect on myself - give me a moment after opening, then ask again.","kappa":"5e6bdf9aef17ddc8aa34e502f73f2ca03f90f561e444deac816b99d3ece87486","bytes":39402,"secs":6.32},{"text":"I reflected, but I don't have a revision worth proposing yet - I'll keep learning from our conversations.","kappa":"c09e187a7ed375bfa84ddacff8babfefd5f6fe4cd57cef5424bc90ef980464ea","bytes":35726,"secs":5.6},{"text":"My self-evolution is switched off right now.","kappa":"ceab6192a5a936eda951f8929afa08beba1c94d76830e042e7fd6966c235be9f","bytes":14311,"secs":2.24},{"text":"There's nothing to roll back - no revision is in force.","kappa":"89627fcc9ab1645e956accb27a23cf2c55f12d9e88f2bab2e65ff13900380b5d","bytes":17324,"secs":2.72},{"text":"Rolled back - I'm exactly as I was before that revision. The old version was never destroyed, so nothing was lost.","kappa":"861fb447b753a86cfab9e0669dad17c20eb1ca14bbd774b169315921273c14fe","bytes":37783,"secs":6.08},{"text":"When should I remind you to","kappa":"da1c6b5daa167a89fa2e2a3192222ea2c343476f99fb19b7a669ff7c5154d14f","bytes":9068,"secs":1.44},{"text":"? Say something like \"in 20 minutes\" or \"at 6\".","kappa":"291b61956fefd360383fc95b3ed24b0e08d692fefa0aef07cb4506980e34511f","bytes":19771,"secs":3.12},{"text":"Done - I'll remind you to","kappa":"61d0755a3435fd422cb3af63922af05c9c5aee543b130bab7628120d9074a76a","bytes":12262,"secs":1.92},{"text":"Cancelled - I won't remind you to","kappa":"533c604e42553aec144b118406e5f399799b4210f924593004ae70499a4fa752","bytes":12646,"secs":2},{"text":"I looked at my own recent failures and drafted a revision of how I should be with you: \"","kappa":"528c174fe6986f1b0b56ee219abdee2ccb3179bedf26ce280baf411405819d23","bytes":27007,"secs":4.4},{"text":"\" - nothing changes unless you say \"approve the revision\". You can always \"roll back your evolution\".","kappa":"9d20386e0dfad3e42bad5894f35a00b4fa9ee1ba48b9be6fd0bb53674180011d","bytes":30725,"secs":4.96},{"text":"Done - the revision is in force, ratified by you. I'll be a little different now: \"","kappa":"73150a617ff3f4d019850d3364e8e76e44aee2e8b8cfbd561c92803f587ab3c8","bytes":27389,"secs":4.4},{"text":"\". Say \"roll back your evolution\" any time.","kappa":"4cef2e084d77806129db9bcd12e4e5d5a52cbaf7a1749c823489d11d2b0f2cad","bytes":16274,"secs":2.56}]}